it.ozimov.cirneco.hamcrest.java8

Class J8Matchers

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.ozimov.cirneco.hamcrest.java7.J7Matchers
      • it.ozimov.cirneco.hamcrest.java8.J8Matchers

  • public class J8Matchers
extends J7Matchers
    The J8Matchers class groups all the matchers from {J7Matchers} plus the new ones introduced by Cirneco's Hamcrest extension for Java 8. Suggested use would be to import all the static methods of this class in a unit tes.
    Since:
    version 0.1 for JDK8
